{% extends 'app.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}Singing Jobs, singers wanted from around the world{% endblock %}

{% block description %}Singers wanted for singing jobs around the world. Music producers looking for singers who want to work and collaborate with. Simply just audition online!{% endblock %}

{% block javascript %}

<script type="text/javascript" src="{{ asset('js/jquery.geocomplete.min.js') }}"></script>

    <script>
        $('#geo-location').geocomplete({
            details: "#search-form",
            types: ['(cities)'],
            blur: true,
            detailsAttribute: "data-geo"
        });
    </script>

{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-8 page-content">
        <h1>Singing Jobs Around the World</h1>

        <h2>About Vocalizr and its Benefits</h2>
        
        <p>Vocalizr is a platform that was created with the aim to connect vocalists and producers worldwide. It is a wonderful place for music production, as the singers
            can find talented producers from worldwide in order to develop a collaboration that would help them become well-known for their talents.
            There are plenty of benefits to enjoy when using vocalizr to find a suitable job for you as a singer:</p>
        
        <ul>
            <li>You have the opportunity to find talented producers to work with, in order to put your talents and qualities in the light</li>
            <li>Vocalizr is a safe and secure online workspace, where you can find a suitable job for your talents</li>
            <li>You can start collaboration with producers worldwide in a remote studio</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>Using vocalizr is simple, as you only need to create your account and start looking for <strong>singing jobs</strong> that suit you.</p>

        <h2>Singers Wanted for Huge Range of Jobs</h2>

        <p>There are a wide range of singing jobs available on vocalizr, so the first step is to create your account and start looking for the 
            jobs that state singers wanted.When you are looking for singing jobs on vocalizr, you will go to the <a href="/gig-hunter">Gig Hunter</a> page,
            where you can look for the jobs that are most suitable for you.</p>
        
        <p>You can refine your search using the search window located on the page, where you can make your custom search for singing jobs, so that you will
            only be shown the jobs that are most suitable for you. There, you can choose between a range of options, so that you can get the results 
            that are most suitable for your needs:</p>
        
        <ul>
            <li>Keywords â€“ add your keywords that you consider most suitable for the job you are interested in</li>
            <li>Select the budget range</li>
            <li>Choose the gender that the job is looking to hire</li>
            <li>Choose the genres</li>
            <li>Vocal characteristics required by the job</li>
            <li>Vocal styles required by the job</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>You will see that there are a variety of singing jobs available, from which you can choose the ones that interest you. Once you find a gig that
            you are interested in and that suits your talents and your genre, you can place your bid for the gig and then the only thing 
            left is to wait for the producer to select you! For any gig, you will see there is a period of time left for the bids to be placed.</p>
        

        <p>There are many <strong>singers wanted</strong> on vocalizr and it does not matter where in the world you are, because with this platform, you can start a collaboration 
            with producers worldwide, due to the opportunity to work in a remote studio. You only need to get your account 
            and start looking for the singing jobs available in order to find the one that suits you. However, you might need to place bids
            on multiple jobs, as the number of singers and of jobs is huge!</p>
        
        
        <p>&nbsp;</p>
        <p><a href="{{ path('gig_hunter') }}" class="btn btn-primary">Find Work Now!</a></p>
</div>
    
    <div class="col-sm-4">
        <div class="search-panel panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                SINGER JOBS
            </div>
            <div class="panel-body padding">
                <form action="{{ path('gig_hunter', {filter: app.request.get('filter')} ) }}" method="get" novalidate>
                <div class="row form-group">
                    <div class="col-sm-12">
                        {{ form_row(form.keywords) }}
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <hr>
                
                <div class="row form-group">
                    <div class="col-sm-12">
                        {{ form_row(form.budget) }}
                    </div>
                </div>
                    
                <hr>
                
                <div class="row form-group">
                    <div class="col-sm-12">
                        {{ form_row(form.gender) }}
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <hr>
                
                <div class="row form-group">
                    <div class="col-sm-12">
                        <input type="checkbox" name="{{ form.studio_access.vars.full_name }}" value="1"{% if form.vars.value.studio_access %} checked{% endif %}> Must have studio access
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <hr>
                
                <div class="row form-group">
                    <div class="col-sm-12">
                        {{ form_row(form.genre) }}
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <hr>
                
                <div class="row form-group">
                    <div class="col-sm-12">
                        {{ form_row(form.vocal_characteristic) }}
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="row form-group">
                    <div class="col-sm-12">
                        {{ form_row(form.vocal_style) }}
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <hr>
                
                <div class="form-buttons">
                    <button type="submit" name="search" value="SEARCH" class="btn btn-sm btn-default">SEARCH</button>
                    <a href="{{ path('gig_hunter') }}" class="btn btn-sm btn-default reset">RESET</a>
                </div>
                {{ form_row(form._token) }}
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
                    {% endblock %}